Test project that uses the security.shiro.filter.config setting and the old database realm (that uses Rel linking tables).

Before running the tests you must execute:

    grails shiro-old-realm-quick-start --prefix="org.example.auth."

Why?

This sets up the older style db model with

- 'User',
- 'Role',
- 'Permission',
- 'RolePermissionRel',
- 'UserRoleRel',
- 'UserPermissionRel'